{"tid":82450,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"Dear 禎 - 破產只得我共你","createTime":"2017-01-16T03:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T14:56:47.000Z","uid":72532,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4de12bd6f45654d7fd620989463bb62489f5da9","tid":82450,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"Dear 禎 - 破產只得我共你<br />\n#哪裡只得我共你<br />\n#DearJane #陳詠謙 #關禮琛<br />\n<br />\n我未醉　但結局已爛尾　無成本　誰談起<br />\n放大假　學接受我共你　人無知　不起<br />\n<br />\n我們　拉起你的短裙<br />\n酒不喝至清晨　可否博好感<br />\n<br />\n＊要再一次眾籌　窮途無路之後<br />\n　就認我也想走　帶著你走　出支那　找匹馬<br />\n　無謂強留　徒添幾百萬傷口<br />\n　望著我的薪酬　快到手卻全然沒收<br />\n　交低門匙　你破產　我破產　都失救<br />\n<br />\n買電腦　合算又有道理　無成本　才狂喜<br />\n趁外界　未隔絕我共你　才無知　得起<br />\n<br />\n我們　身邊太多批評<br />\n只需倆口不認　他終記不清<br />\n<br />\nRepeat ＊<br />\n<br />\n哪怕無人在乎你　我倆要愛惜自己<br />\n怕抗爭都很怕死　要坐的士也合理<br />\n要過渡破產危機<br />\n<br />\nRepeat ＊<br />\n<br />\n當然　快破產　嚇到死　都失救"},{"pid":"e5cc87828560d9f352affe675c5191d8fef7119d","tid":82450,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34110976e402294d3a1e8844ac340902e73c9fb9","tid":82450,"uid":71960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:08:47.000Z","msg":"有啲唔係太啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1839893f741d6ca8a4b9c3a25bf0506be9a0922","tid":82450,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲唔係太啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪眾籌嗰兩隻字"},{"pid":"c205ef4f4ac30c0daf94763aefa7d6726d631933","tid":82450,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"好似有d怪，但都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw好皮比你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfd3c58